灭绝”，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/killer-mike">杀手迈克</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-stipe">迈克尔·斯蒂普</a>等人则<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-michael-stipe-killer-mike-more-sign-open-letter-joe-biden-gaza-ceasefire-3522135">给拜登总统写了一封公开信，</a>要求“立即缓和冲突并停火”。加沙和以色列，以免又一个生命丧生。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gal-gadot">盖尔·加朵</a>(Gal Gadot)、克里斯·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-pine">派恩 (Chris Pine)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-hamill">马克·哈米尔 (Mark Hamill</a> ) 和杰米·李·柯蒂斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-lee-curtis">Jamie Lee Curtis)</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/hollywood-stars-sign-open-letter-support-israel-3514639">等 700 名好莱坞明星签署了一封公开信，表达对以色列的支持，</a>而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/selena-gomez">赛琳娜·戈麦斯 (Selena Gomez</a> ) 的化妆品公司 Rare Beauty 则宣布将向以色列<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/selena-gomez-makeup-brand-to-donate-funds-to-the-gaza-relief-efforts-3534155">的救援工作捐款。加沙。</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tilda-swinton-steve-coogan-and-massive-attacks-robert-del-naja-among-2000-artists-calling-for-gaza-ceasefire-in-open-letter-3516616">来自艺术界的 2000 多名人士</a>，包括蒂尔达·斯文顿 (Tilda Swinton)、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/massive-attack">Massive Attack</a>的罗伯特·德尔·纳贾 (Robert Del Naja) 和米里亚姆·马戈伊尔斯 (Miriam Margoyles) 签署了一封公开信，呼吁停火。</p><p>同样，麦当娜<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-on-israel-hamas-conflict-how-can-human-beings-be-so-cruel-to-one-another-3518887">在 O2 舞台上谈到了这一情况</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-morello">汤姆·莫雷洛</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-morello-calls-for-condemnation-of-harm-to-all-children-no-matter-who-they-are-after-jamie-lee-curtis-deletes-photo-of-palestinians-3513188">则呼吁谴责对所有儿童的伤害，</a> “无论他们是谁”。</p><p>最近，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-vylan">鲍勃·维兰 (Bob Vylan)</a>指责<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sleaford-mods">Sleaford Mods</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">IDLES</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-vylan-call-out-cowardly-sleaford-mods-and-idles-for-not-speaking-out-on-palestine-3536053">没有公开支持巴勒斯坦。</a></p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/benefits-share-powerful-statement-on-armistice-day-and-the-israel-palestine-war-3536251">《福利》在停战日和以色列-巴勒斯坦战争上发表了强有力的声明，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
